{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/11514", "repo": "rails", "body": "Which critical information will get exposed?\r\n\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\n if Rails.env.development?\r\n          app.routes.append do\r\n            get '/rails/info/properties' => \"rails/info#properties\"\r\n            get '/rails/info/routes' => \"rails/info#routes\"\r\n            get '/rails/info' => \"rails/info#index\"\r\n          end\r\n        end\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nas you may notice, the critical information such ruby version etc will only\r\nbe available in `/rails/info/` routes which are only defined in\r\ndevelopment.\r\n\r\nthis static page exists in all rails version < 4. And gets displayed both production & development Envs even today.", "_id": {"$oid": "5237d3a8bd3543c151007fc4"}, "issue_id": 11514, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/21342961", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/11514#issuecomment-21342961", "updated_at": "2013-07-22T13:20:21Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gaurish/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gaurish/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gaurish/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gaurish/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/gaurish", "login": "gaurish", "gravatar_id": "cb0b42e452cd13d469565a23a8abe441", "html_url": "https://github.com/gaurish", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gaurish/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gaurish/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gaurish/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/cb0b42e452cd13d469565a23a8abe441?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F58861ae4fb7b472c95e64685229ad9ed.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gaurish/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 235844, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gaurish/followers", "type